-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/copper-declines-in-london-as-china-s-economy-slows-lme-preview.html
Copper dropped in London as the
economy in China, the world’s biggest user of the metal,
expanded at the slowest pace in a year and the dollar rebounded.  Market News:  Metals News:  To contact the reporter on this story:
